### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

### Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me

### List Rooms
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms?page=1&limit=10

### Get Single Room
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/room_id_here

### Create Room (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

{
  "name": "Luxury Suite",
  "description": "Premium room with all amenities",
  "price": 200,
  "capacity": 2,
  "amenities": ["WiFi", "TV", "Minibar", "Jacuzzi"]
}

### Checkout
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

{
  "roomId": "room_id_here",
  "checkIn": "2024-12-20",
  "checkOut": "2024-12-22",
  "guests": 2
}

### Get User Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
